01:28:27,046 --> 01:28:29,309
and see so many
board feet of timber...

1068
01:28:29,380 --> 01:28:32,043
couldn't look
at a beaver lodge
and see so many pelts.

1069
01:28:32,113 --> 01:28:34,277
now i saw little miracles.

1070
01:28:36,411 --> 01:28:39,541
we have a wheel
that takes you
from here to there.

1071
01:28:39,611 --> 01:28:43,542
but they have a wheel
that takes you to the stars.

1072
01:28:47,768 --> 01:28:49,526

1073
01:28:50,088 --> 01:28:53,208

1074
01:29:07,875 --> 01:29:10,937
old indian: soaring eagle
knew he had lost his place.

1075
01:29:11,008 --> 01:29:13,271
for the first time
in his life,

1076
01:29:13,341 --> 01:29:15,173
he knew the true meaning
of fear.

1077
01:29:18,807 --> 01:29:21,704
and loved by the buffalo
left his family

1078
01:29:21,774 --> 01:29:24,836
so that he might live
for all the people.

1079
01:29:24,908 --> 01:29:27,504
this was the price
of his gift--

1080
01:29:27,574 --> 01:29:29,138
to pursue his journey

1081
01:29:29,206 --> 01:29:32,969
to change the terrible vision
of growling bear.

